sentences: Michael Marquez (born July 8, 1982), better known by his stage name Mike Mictlan ([ˈmikt͡ɬaːn]), is a rapper from Los Angeles, California, who is currently based in Minneapolis, Minnesota.
Michael Marquez (born July 8, 1982), better known by his stage name Mike Mictlan ([ˈmikt͡ɬaːn]), is a rapper from Los Angeles, California, who is currently based in Minneapolis, Minnesota.
Mike Mictlan has released four solo albums and is currently signed to Doomtree Records.
City Pages listed him as the 10th best Minnesota rapper in 2012.
By the time Marquez reached his teenage years, he was sent to live with his uncle in Minneapolis, Minnesota.
